### Product Search API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

# ============ SEARCH ENDPOINTS ============

### 1. Search products by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?q=shirt

### 2. Search products (another example)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?q=phone

### 3. Search with empty query (should return empty array)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?q=

# ============ GET ALL PRODUCTS WITH FILTERS ============

### 4. Get all products (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 5. Get products with search term
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?searchTerm=laptop

### 6. Get products by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=Electronics

### 7. Get products by category and subcategory
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=Fashion&subCategory=Shirts

### 8. Get products with price range
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?minPrice=100&maxPrice=500

### 9. Get products sorted by price (low to high)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc

### 10. Get products sorted by price (high to low)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sortBy=price&sortOrder=desc

### 11. Get products with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=5

### 12. Combined filters: category + price range + sorting + pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=Electronics&minPrice=50&maxPrice=1000&sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc&page=1&limit=10

### 13. Search with all filters combined
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?searchTerm=wireless&category=Electronics&minPrice=20&maxPrice=200&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=12
